Output example/tapes/output/print_key.gif

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 800
Set Height 450
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.0

Type "fvm dart run tool/bin/print_key.dill"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type "a"
Sleep 200ms
Type "b"
Sleep 200ms
Type "c"
Sleep 200ms
Up
Sleep 200ms
Down
Sleep 200ms
Tab
Sleep 200ms
Escape
Sleep 500ms
